description.title: Letterboxd 500 most watched movies of all time
subtitle: Updated as of: April 4th, 2025
Hope you all enjoy and let me know if a movie is missing :)
Percentage watched by me: 55%.
* Barbie is #1 with 5,18M views
* Dirty Dancing is #500 with 1,01M views
Monthly changes:
* Conclave (#394) and Enola Holmes (#498) are new on this list. Carrie and mother! are out
* Anora (+138), The Substance (+18), Wicked (+14), Notting Hill (+14), How to Lose a Guy in 10 Days (+13), Beautiful Boy (+13) and Nosferatu (+12) gained the most spots
* Logan (-11), Booksmart (-9), Birdman (-9), BlacKkKlansman (-9), Midnight in Paris (-9) and Borat (-9) lost the most spots
Movies that are close to an entrance:
* Ford v Ferrari (1M views)
* Hotel Transylvania (1M views)
* Carrie (1M views)
* mother! (999K views)
* John Wick: Chapter 4 (997K views)
Trending movies that will sooner or later be in this list:
* Grave of the Fireflies (993K views)
* The Wild Robot (927K views)
* Trap (881K views)
